      "ref": "1",
      "heading": "Apostles' Creed",
      "html": "<div class=\"lib-creed\">\n<p>\n<strong>I believe in God the Father Almighty,</strong>\n          Maker of heaven and earth.\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 1:1\">Gen. 1:1</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 6:9\">Matt. 6:9</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>And in Jesus Christ, his only Son, our Lord;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"John 3:16\">John 3:16</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 1:4\">Rom. 1:4</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n          who was <strong>conceived by the Holy Ghost,</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 1:35\">Luke 1:35</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>born of the Virgin Mary;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 1:18\">Matt. 1:18–23</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Galatians 4:4\">Gal. 4:4</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>suffered under Pontius Pilate,</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Mark 15:15\">Mark 15:15</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>was crucified, dead, and buried;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 5:8\">Rom. 5:8</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 15:3\">1 Cor. 15:3</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>he descended into hell;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Peter 3:19\">1 Pet. 3:19</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ephesians 4:9\">Eph. 4:9</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>the third day he rose again from the dead;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 15:4\">1 Cor. 15:4</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 24:6\">Luke 24:6</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>he ascended into heaven,</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 1:9\">Acts 1:9</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n          and <strong>sitteth on the right hand of God the Father Almighty;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hebrews 1:3\">Heb. 1:3</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalm 110:1\">Ps. 110:1</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n          from thence <strong>he shall come to judge the quick and the dead.</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 17:31\">Acts 17:31</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Timothy 4:1\">2 Tim. 4:1</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>I believe in the Holy Ghost;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"John 14:26\">John 14:26</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 2:4\">Acts 2:4</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>the holy catholic Church;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ephesians 1:22-23\">Eph. 1:22–23</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Matthew 16:18\">Matt. 16:18</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>the communion of saints;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 12:12\">1 Cor. 12:12–13</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hebrews 12:22-23\">Heb. 12:22–23</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>the forgiveness of sins;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ephesians 1:7\">Eph. 1:7</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 10:43\">Acts 10:43</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n<strong>the resurrection of the body;</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Corinthians 15:42-44\">1 Cor. 15:42–44</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"John 5:28-29\">John 5:28–29</a>)\n        </p>\n<p>\n          and the <strong>life everlasting. Amen.</strong>\n          (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"John 17:3\">John 17:3</a>;\n          <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 John 5:11\">1 John 5:11</a>)\n        </p>\n</div>"
    }
  ]
}
